{
  "texts": [
    "Tapilot-Crossing aims to build a benchmark for real-world data analysis.",
    "An issue that cannot be overlooked is the quality of these datasets.",
    "Wretblad et al.",
    "conduct a thorough analysis of the NL2SQL dataset BIRD [101], discovering inaccuracies in some of the gold SQLs and noise within certain NL queries [109].",
    "The creators of the BIRD dataset introduce this noise during the dataset creation process."
  ]
}